ke.go.moh.oec
Class RequestTypeId

java.lang.Object
  ke.go.moh.oec.RequestTypeId

public class RequestTypeId
extends java.lang.Object

Define data request type IDs for the getData() method of the IService interface.

These are defined as integers, rather than an enumerated type, to avoid problems of compatibility between versions of the OEC library. This allows a client to build against an old version of the library but use a new version of the library where additional request type IDs have been defined.

Author:
Jim Grace
